{"tid":306554,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"小明參加了七一愛國遊行","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T07:43:38.000Z","uid":43751,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4b876d47cbddf7704be8d414b3cf5f67de477e","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"朋友阿發介紹一單好兼職<br />\n&ldquo;兩點到五點 留tg&rdquo;<br />\n阿發想去 但無膽 找小明作伴"},{"pid":"4c20c334f4caf88678a5123b0235987762db9975","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"tg :<br />\nhi i am 李小明，想參加遊行，再帶多一個朋友<br />\n<br />\n回覆:<br />\n小明<br />\n我想同你玩一個七十二小時既遊戲<br />\n七一見"},{"pid":"e0f121d49e90c85074b0391b76e8fbb6c8f1ba52","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"七一小明和阿發一起集合<br />\n<br />\n現場有很多志同道合的朋友"},{"pid":"aa3b3aaadcce6c200bab02e304b660600c2c93aa","tid":306554,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"係小明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f254321709edf926dffd01405aacb18455af5c6","tid":306554,"uid":59573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d61fb8b81e72448c9d515fe093fdfc06611d116","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"到最後<br />\n搞手沒有出現 沒有錢派<br />\n阿發問:小明小明 我們怎麼辦?<br />\n小明大喊:我叫了你多少次不要喊我的名字!<br />\n<br />\n在場的愛國人仕都知小明的真正身份<br />\n令小明尷尬"},{"pid":"e53666aed53bcb00851b767f2d7b443eb4daf638","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:48:28.000Z","msg":"小明告訴各位<br />\n立即用tg狂炸搞手<br />\n搞手設立了一個大騙局<br />\n一定會在現場觀看自己的完美作品"},{"pid":"a62d219213ccc7d43657d48d42dd5de991e6cd9b","tid":306554,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"138952dbdc54c3e1833180eba28ed4d331e14f00","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;只要你發覺誰的電影狂響就知誰是搞手&rdquo;<br />\n小明說<br />\n<br />\n但沒有電話狂響"},{"pid":"d3dec4171e21944921021017206e1c2ebd2e28c7","tid":306554,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"變左偵探故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3565727a1ef7ca8535597ddde4e57a8674ab2f","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"最後沒有結果<br />\n各人帶著失望和五星旗回去"},{"pid":"8043bd28d79f051a78307ba7d57bfa9b23f9a3cf","tid":306554,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"Live 文"},{"pid":"3550400095025d91f7a5d0fedfdf7b8c21c366a0","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"阿發拍了拍小明的肩膀<br />\n說&ldquo;別失望&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明一手怒推開<br />\n大嗌&ldquo;妖 你係基咋 我唔係呀&rdquo;<br />\n每個人都望向阿發<br />\n認為他是基的<br />\n<br />\n阿發好尷尬<br />\n小明說:對不起 我今天的尿好黃"},{"pid":"3bd79ccd2bf64aebcd027c0be768c3ebb95e232c","tid":306554,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"等到小明了"},{"pid":"3a652437d5dea3ecadbbabd5baf5fe151100aee1","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"等大夥兒走了<br />\n小明跟蹤其中一個愛國人 戴口罩的<br />\n到了馬路邊<br />\n愛國人就在安全島上<br />\n和小明隔一條馬路<br />\n而湊巧 安全島上也站著阿發<br />\n兩人吐著遊行被騙的苦水"},{"pid":"315681a8f82cec8641f3e47a6d5ec41f1c4cf479","tid":306554,"uid":122566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:01:02.000Z","msg":"暗戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb7bd28598f8a387267057dc87b2e7a968c720e","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"小明大嗌 &ldquo;阿發捉住他 他就是搞手&rdquo;<br />\n阿發立即做了<br />\n<br />\n搞手說:小明你果然是高手<br />\n<br />\n阿發兩手擒著搞手<br />\n口中喃喃說:死啦 痴線佬遇著痴線佬<br />\n<br />\n小明說:每個人也拿出電話用tg，當然你也有，但每個人也上連登尋搞手，唯獨你一個人沒有開連登。一個年輕人怎會不上連登。你有上，但因為你是搞手，所以不能出post追討，別人看見你的account name ，我有錯嗎?"},{"pid":"105feb2c66df760b6564a58ac14563e5cc43f38a","tid":306554,"uid":14979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:06:53.000Z","msg":"變左偵探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2acda61b21ebd282072e5825a796394f326656","tid":306554,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"好好獎勵他"},{"pid":"dcaa65725432b24e5b6bc26a8ec17ffc2e86594a","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我想跟你玩一個七十二小時的遊戲&rdquo;，搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;怎樣玩呀?我已經出post說我已經捉住你，所有愛國青年都跑過來殺死你了&rdquo;，小明說<br />\n<br />\n搞手用九牛二虎之力甩開右手<br />\n但還是被阿發按在地上<br />\n搞手發難不是為了逃走<br />\n而是拋了一個小盒小在馬路中間<br />\n<br />\n可惜紅燈車多<br />\n小明想過去幫手<br />\n但行車阻止小明"},{"pid":"9fe28a0f3689116aeab8ccba5c9f18c4f6193e63","tid":306554,"uid":4696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好好獎勵他</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d2415906bd8c483df01a4212faca704b154c91","tid":306554,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:09:12.000Z","msg":"小明故緊係要留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e40ef2a834d6f2cdb3b0aeb8439d8dd9edcce61","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"搞手微微笑著<br />\n向阿發說:你看見盒上的圖案嗎?<br />\n<br />\n阿發說:噢嘈糕了 是iphone的盒子<br />\n<br />\n搞手說:黃啟發 那是一部iphone 價值不只二千元"},{"pid":"59e314d4135dcdee6e1278c433499da132e8a39c","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"搞手說:你不放開我 就會看著那iphone粉碎了<br />\n<br />\n小明隔著一條馬路說:拿一個爛盒叫我相信入面有iphone?<br />\n<br />\n搞手下巴被阿發按在地上說:不相信，等它被貨車碾碎你就知道了"},{"pid":"19ceaba069902daccece4592b77854f5f4cb7a42","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"我信，黃啟發大嗌<br />\n<br />\n小明說:是假的!<br />\n<br />\n發問:你怎知道呀"},{"pid":"98a5d97ed905e454f42c9fc271c4e6d781e4bccb","tid":306554,"uid":45028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1da82f0654a3ebe749ba4f94b428e5217fa4ae","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"小明說:你就相信我一次行不行?<br />\n<br />\n發說:為什麼相信你不信他?"},{"pid":"cf52aaa3cce9fc1fb39bf82339ade118b528ef1d","tid":306554,"uid":20517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"Live <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672806bb15e4aa53ffcc228b0afd5b93f948da88","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"阿發放手的話，你們得眼白白看我走了。搞手說<br />\n<br />\n身為連登你，你能不能有骨氣一點?小明問發<br />\n<br />\n發說:有骨氣的話我就不出來遊行了"},{"pid":"07ccb13505cfd4e303fcaf331105c29c58cfe782","tid":306554,"uid":74790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d09c784d80482e3610f43e944375a8cf009a84","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"阿發放手了<br />\n搞手跑了走<br />\n<br />\n阿發拾起iphone<br />\n小明拆開包裝<br />\n&ldquo;喂喂&rdquo;小明壓著情緒 抖震地說&ldquo;這是什麼&rdquo;<br />\n阿發一聲&ldquo;吓!?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">甘大枝呀</span>"},{"pid":"e13cfcf19706713c788c277e9ce2af2292391aaa","tid":306554,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"執個跌左落地既iphone都好似無間道咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信我<br />\n唔好信佢<br />\n真係唔信？"},{"pid":"96eac2a77370c1ba4726230336ee3d3c0780b369","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"然後小明追逐搞手到人群中<br />\n小明搭著搞手的肩 笑說:真有緣我們又見面<br />\n<br />\n搞手說:真能幹 和你玩遊戲真榮幸<br />\n<br />\n小明說: 能走出我五指山 當你贏<br />\n<br />\n搞手問:你知道我們到了什麼地方?<br />\n<br />\n小明說:愛國者的地盤。我也愛國的，雖然是因為錢。<br />\n<br />\n搞手說:你看看你背上貼了什麼<br />\n<br />\n小明一驚，回頭一看，&ldquo;我要真普選&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n定神過來，已經被藍絲打了一拳"},{"pid":"9cd5ab4ca6a19b9a2dc2ae38e87560601b516b32","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:50:17.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;有時一加一不等於二 試想想搞手如此做 一定不會是蛇頭把人頭費一千元吞了的&rdquo;小明向愛國者們說<br />\n<br />\n阿發卻向愛國者說&ldquo;要不是小明衝動 私自行動 我們一等人早就捉著了搞手了 我已經容忍小明很多次 不是第一次了&rdquo;"},{"pid":"d61830880081d5e0d476509fdff694742b86b363","tid":306554,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"屌你暗戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70ed9d3cf6c754f947b1d6f6eaa58e91d6d62d2","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我是愛國組高級督察黃啟發，立即磅水投行，否則後果自負&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n搞手遞出手機 展現所有愛國組成員的照片<br />\n<br />\n阿發說:有事慢談呀大俠，我是來跟你談判的，你要錢，我們給你錢好了，不要放我們的樣貌上網。<br />\n<br />\n搞手說:你的聲音好難聽，叫小明來跟我談判。"},{"pid":"1ea2612574b1b524405a388843696eb2a4d687a2","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;小明，搞手約了我們在mcdonald談判，請你快一點到&rdquo;阿發致電小明<br />\n<br />\n小明說&ldquo;千萬不要給他說話，我們只要捉著他就好，不要中他的圈套&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我已經跟他談判了，他說只要跟你談&rdquo;發說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我頂&rdquo;小明說<br />\n<br />\n發大嗌，&ldquo;難道撞口撞面一句話不講嗎?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n其實阿發打算杯葛小明，不讓小明插水，想不到卻墮入了搞手的圈套"},{"pid":"c76533f3584a87c3b303354316f75a090ebec3ca","tid":306554,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fb4c84df7b73feae2ffc978dbb32c6d61f9c21","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"搞手跟小明對談<br />\n搞手說:這八達通給你了<br />\n小明接下了<br />\n小明說:為什麼要放你走?<br />\n搞手說:我有你們遊行的照片嘛<br />\n小明說:我不怕<br />\n搞手說:你要知道七十二小時的遊戲玩什麼嗎?想玩下去嗎<br />\n小明沒出聲<br />\n<br />\n搞手輕輕離開了<br />\n小明一個人坐在m記"},{"pid":"51220b64177392208f88228be396251669a76dd3","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"阿發衝入m記大罵<br />\n&ldquo;我們都給他放上網了，他人呢?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n放走了<br />\n<br />\n阿發大怒 卻無可奈何"},{"pid":"dc30aab6a0c511baa7c004f599d8c1a6fd55a316","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"這單醜聞放於網上<br />\n很快成為焦點了<br />\n<br />\n小明不介意成為主角之一<br />\n反而傳媒發現了奇怪一點<br />\n原來出席者有一個叫歐陽修的人<br />\n而歐陽修的老爸，歐陽橋卻是政黨&ldquo;愛黨力量&rdquo;的主席<br />\n這次兒子收錢遊行，把愛黨力量的架子丟光了"},{"pid":"694b190804ebd2637eea00449bf7505de45a4bb9","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:00:23.000Z","msg":"小明叫阿發查了愛黨力量的資料<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;明明當日遊行就沒有看見歐陽修，為什麼要駕禍於他?&rdquo;小明問<br />\n<br />\n阿發說&ldquo;算了吧，你的時間不多了，放過兇手吧&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明費解<br />\n<br />\n阿發拿出一包藥說&ldquo;你在m記掉下的，我查過是末期癌症藥&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n阿發說&ldquo;對不起，但你常常當面罵我也有不對嘛。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明說&ldquo;西藥太躁嘛&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明知道藥是屬於搞手的<br />\n<br />\n小明更期待這個七十二小時的遊戲"},{"pid":"13e08bb64cd1282c02e06ad6431b2687cc44647d","tid":306554,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b5f0e0197ba9d0af875331ce91056b4772f26b","tid":306554,"uid":4648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:01:55.000Z","msg":"暗戰小明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9814a6a9456c55d4db417f1fc4173db6535897","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;常常見到你哦，你叫什麼名字&rdquo; 女人說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;知道我叫什麼名字對你沒好處&rdquo; 搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我不是求好處的&rdquo;女人說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;可惜我沒有時間&rdquo; 搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有時間會做什麼?&rdquo; 女人說<br />\n<br />\n搞手咳了一口血，&ldquo;對不起，我先走了，再見&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們是不是不會再見面了&rdquo;，女人問<br />\n<br />\n搞手回頭，&ldquo;只是今輩子罷了&rdquo;"},{"pid":"43b9db6bc4b72a9dfbd4be90c4b1fddc1839a4b3","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:14:21.000Z","msg":"小明決定夜闖愛黨力量<br />\n走到門口<br />\n卻要密碼開鎖<br />\n小明沒有頭緒<br />\n想起搞手給自己的八達通<br />\n一放上感影器<br />\n開門了"},{"pid":"9734e0d9831479ef33f394f0ad21a649b6eecb17","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:17:19.000Z","msg":"小明進入愛黨力量<br />\n在黑暗中用電筒照射<br />\n查了一會兒<br />\n無頭緒<br />\n根本不清楚這七十二小時的遊戲玩什麼<br />\n只看見了很多中國主席來香港的行程<br />\n小明覺得或者跟國家主席有關<br />\n但不清楚<br />\n<br />\n特然光明了<br />\n小明立即躲入枱底<br />\n愛黨力量的人知道有人闖入自己的基地<br />\n都搜索入侵者"},{"pid":"4517d4636d30aed0af0fcaebe4ba9d7ecd2ff606","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:20:01.000Z","msg":"小明偷偷的地溜出門外<br />\n想跑樓梯走<br />\n卻聽見有人跑上來<br />\n沒有去路<br />\n<br />\n電話響起<br />\n搞手說&ldquo;搭升降機&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明說&ldquo;升降機?更危險哦，一定有人防守&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n搞手說:相信我吧，我們是隊友來的"},{"pid":"1ba03becacd46f5174183493c08c90dcfa7836b1","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:22:49.000Z","msg":"小明進入了升降機，問&ldquo;為什麼不啟動的，你是不是給鎖上了?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n搞手說&ldquo;你給升降機的感應器擋著了，傻西&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明啟動了升降機，只希望它能送自己安全離開"},{"pid":"eb11a71dce03047f726b03e20aa96fd27902b816","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:24:07.000Z","msg":"升降機在半空中停下了<br />\n<br />\n小明心想<br />\n<br />\n今次仆街了"},{"pid":"5f3f068648badc6f66bbebe3818f93fd17382f2b","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:27:27.000Z","msg":"所有愛黨力量的人都衝向升降機<br />\n搞手這刻才動身<br />\n慢慢走入愛黨力量的總部<br />\n把東西拿走<br />\n<br />\n總部內一個人地沒有<br />\n都去擒拿了小明"},{"pid":"33b14ab305b4ccb526dd339450caca5a0846b559","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"小明卡在二十三樓<br />\n只聽見門外有不少人<br />\n打算撬開升降機門<br />\n要把小明殺了<br />\n<br />\n小明凶多吉少"},{"pid":"6758daa68dabdc99b5e9e014973d752c10e7d2d7","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:33:55.000Z","msg":"小明電話響了<br />\n搞手打來<br />\n搞手說:你求我，我便來救你。救你的風險很大。<br />\n<br />\n小明:我求你救我。<br />\n<br />\n搞手說，你打開升降機頂，爬出機箱，然後會看見隔離另一條升降機吊纜，然後會有另一架升降機接你走的"},{"pid":"c0bc381b1899501444bf3506aa7fd4a0b081b31d","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:37:47.000Z","msg":"搞入離開了愛黨力量的四十八層<br />\n坐二號升降機<br />\n停在二十二樓<br />\n然後聽到天花一聲巨響。<br />\n小明從二十三樓的一號升降機跳上二十二樓的二號機<br />\n滙合了搞手<br />\n<br />\n愛黨力量的人撬開升降機門<br />\n見沒有人 <br />\n見天花頂一個洞<br />\n得知入侵者走失了<br />\n十分勞氣"},{"pid":"b850472cac22d4b82f5866729e6c795c75499818","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:51:14.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;陳為強，當過區議員助理，應該是建制派的接班人，三年前離開了愛黨力量就退隱政界。你以為愛黨力量的人不會懷疑你偷了他們東西嗎?&rdquo;，小明說。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你的資料搜集做得真好&rdquo;，搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你的計算也不錯。搞一個打手遊行吸引我，再故意捏造愛黨力量主席兒子歐陽修也有份參加，令我查上了愛黨力量的總部，然後逼我引開所有人，自己就大搖大擺進入偷東西。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明再補多一句:&ldquo;要不是你快死了，可能會做末來特首，真可惜&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a01106bf2420f96c1ef7ccdfc009534a572f1a44","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:56:41.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;愛黨力量的人，什麼也敢當，這回我大禍臨頭了&rdquo;，小明說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;放心，七十二小時的遊戲，玩贏的話，你就安全了&rdquo;。搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你偷的是什麼?&rdquo;小明問<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;沙林毒氣&rdquo;，搞手答<br />\n<br />\n答案令小明驚訝<br />\n<br />\n小明不想玩了"},{"pid":"7dc0b8ce10047c9bea86e1cc3a42875584cbd9d4","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T19:20:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U1whUBLZLJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU1whUBLZLJQ&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4d1632ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U1whUBLZLJQ</a>"},{"pid":"216f1431df67fd76b4a38cb81c4b2afbc214dd04","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T19:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtube.com/U1whUBLZLJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FU1whUBLZLJQ&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d9083ca8\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/U1whUBLZLJQ</a>"},{"pid":"f53e6518c1b7a0b43cfabb57fda736461bc56c6e","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T19:25:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U1whUBLZLJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU1whUBLZLJQ&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4d1632ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U1whUBLZLJQ</a>"},{"pid":"e532caec6ff95f0dec05ba65a564fda9294f5a87","tid":306554,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"小明玩完了"},{"pid":"fb367edb33100a8aa4a09ea467086be1b630c343","tid":306554,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T22:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5867df77e39cd564e6c739466d4672b86c7ce055","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:28:35.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我係重案組總督察黃啟發，請問歐陽先生，你們的總部被闖入有什麼遺失嗎?&rdquo;阿發問<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你哋啲同事黎問左八千幾次啦，八千幾次啦，無呀&rdquo;，歐陽橋邊說邊震盪著大肚腩。<br />\n<br />\n歐陽在說謊，遺失的東西不能公諸於世"},{"pid":"8c0a71c5eed1b6e220a7c7ca32d626a4d4fa1444","tid":306554,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:29:24.000Z","msg":"你老母重案組督察去為左一千銀遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550121cc3acec5e45d508c5ea5fb07d5e8213e54","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母重案組督察去為左一千銀遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.taicishuo.com/Data/Uploads/image/2015-12-11/566a91b3a1ecc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taicishuo.com%2FData%2FUploads%2Fimage%2F2015-12-11%2F566a91b3a1ecc.jpg&h=65bc991f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15ecb47917da3786b4f5b8b7e256023ef2c34846","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:19:34.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;為什麼我要幫你?我畀一分鐘你說服我，不然我就叫門外的黃啟發進場拉人&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n五十九，五十八，五十七<br />\n<br />\n小明在倒數"},{"pid":"75f49becd85f2b4331852bf8dc1826fe0bc512ce","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:22:49.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;你知道為什麼要在回歸跟你玩嗎?&rdquo;，搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;當然，回歸，國家主席訪港，沙林毒氣。就是說有人要在香港謀殺中國元首&rdquo;，小明推理出來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你不覺得打救國家主席很偉大嗎?&rdquo;，搞手問<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;不覺得。三十七，三十六&rdquo;，小明說"},{"pid":"33cfea251bed8827f05ad1bdec00970928e3bbed","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我無時間了。我想報仇。&rdquo;搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;因為你被愛黨力量趕走?&rdquo;，小明說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;對呀，我要你幫手&rdquo;，搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你的恩怨，與我無關。廿六，廿五，廿四&rdquo;小明在倒數"},{"pid":"1e4dca238460bf7ea32b3772d5159c6adac46c0b","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;沒有你幫助，他們就會搶回沙林毒氣，死很多人，搞政變，天下大亂&rdquo;搞手說<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;不在乎，只想拉到你&rdquo;小明"},{"pid":"b2882e53266b8b323a736632980a565829295bbe","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:36:38.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我覺得這兩日你一條尾，就是一隻狗，被我撚得很快樂&rdquo;，搞手說<br />\n<br />\n小明停止了倒數<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你不想知道我下一步怎麼做嗎?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明指著後門，說&ldquo;你從這邊走&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;好把，讓我明天再撚化你吧&rdquo;，搞手離開了"},{"pid":"21d486037563a1ac78fbc951ae89eb0877ce97b6","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:43:39.000Z","msg":"黃啟發進入餐廳，抱怨對小明說&ldquo;他還未到嗎?這麼不守時的撚樣&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明說&ldquo;他走了&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;走了?!你為什麼不通知我呀&rdquo;，黃啟發說<br />\n<br />\n小明摸摸自己額頭，裝病說&ldquo;對不起，我今天的尿很黃。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n黃啟發一心以為小明有癌症，慚愧於自己脾氣，抱歉地說&ldquo;不要緊，我今天的尿也很黃，熱氣罷了&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;明天有大project ，保你升職&rdquo;，小明說"},{"pid":"8b816ffa9aca61bdefb11c5d2ec274f70d4ab47e","tid":306554,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"對於小明來講<br />\n危險好吸引<br />\n<br />\n沒有是非黑白<br />\n最緊要刺激"},{"pid":"128bbba866e7aae0bb1ffe01b400af4dbdce1b0a","tid":306554,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"暗戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302fa18b8ad802c8988488f9728a51dd7ceeba4e","tid":306554,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"愛黨力量好激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4142a67763abb8284fd5e4b2b6df0f70373c1fc5","tid":306554,"uid":47845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7a0cb9a5902d6429570bbfd690954e78425ab8eb","tid":306554,"uid":117944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T19:02:05.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}